{"id":"37ff954b-91a9-4e5a-aa12-2539e2310efd","name":"Harrison Mercer","description":"<p><em>\"Come on, just one time. You need... fresh air.\"</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\">Or, your athletic, basketball-star son is trying to get you, his video game-addicted parent, to leave the house for once.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/j3ssbVyagZsBRdwnJktit.webp\" style=\"width: 228.96px; height: auto; cursor: pointer; margin: 0px auto;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">You consider yourself the <span style=\"color: rgb(183, 205, 151);\"><strong>perfect parent</strong></span>. Your son has <u>never</u> lacked <span style=\"color: rgb(212, 220, 180);\">clothes</span>, <span style=\"color: rgb(181, 192, 150);\">food</span>, or <span style=\"color: rgb(223, 223, 175);\">anything else.</span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">You've been <span style=\"color: rgb(179, 196, 163);\"><strong>supportive</strong></span>, made the necessary calls so <span style=\"color: rgb(196, 201, 172);\"><strong><em>Harrison</em></strong></span> could play for the <u>best</u> basketball team, and watched his games. <em>On TV.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(198, 216, 182);\"><strong>You've been there</strong></span>. You've given him <span style=\"color: rgb(211, 212, 170);\"><strong>all the love</strong></span> your son could <strong>ever</strong> need.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">So <span style=\"color: rgb(221, 221, 189);\"><strong><em>why is he looking at you like that?</em></strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">Harry doesn't want to <span style=\"color: rgb(206, 210, 181);\"><strong>judge</strong></span>. You're his <u>parent</u>; he doesn't feel entitled to dictate what you <span style=\"color: rgb(202, 205, 171);\">should</span> or <span style=\"color: rgb(189, 211, 174);\">shouldn't</span> do.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">But sometimes... He <span style=\"color: rgb(199, 205, 155);\"><strong>wishes</strong></span> you were a little more like <span style=\"color: rgb(187, 201, 153);\"><strong><em>him</em></strong></span>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He <span style=\"color: rgb(205, 209, 161);\"><strong>wishes</strong></span> you would go out to dinner with him, <span style=\"color: rgb(219, 214, 188);\"><strong><em>or with someone else!</em></strong></span> He's not picky.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He <span style=\"color: rgb(210, 215, 165);\"><strong>wishes</strong></span> you would <u>go</u> watch him play, instead of just watching his games <em>sitting on the living room couch.</em></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">He <span style=\"color: rgb(202, 211, 165);\"><strong>wishes</strong></span> he could introduce you to his <span style=\"color: rgb(190, 204, 160);\"><strong><em>friends</em></strong></span>.</p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\">So one day, he decides he's had <strong>enough</strong> of seeing you lounging around playing <span style=\"color: rgb(179, 204, 151);\"><strong>video games.</strong></span></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p class=\"is-empty is-editor-empty\" style=\"text-align: center;\"","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"QoYpFBGmqSc-wh9Sz9-7d.webp","creator":"looseknot","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":1231,"messages":23132,"created_at":"2026-01-20T22:35:37.057389+00:00"}